{
  "texts": [
    "This benchmark contains 9,693 natural language questions consisting of a training set of 8,659 NL/SPARQL-pairs and a test set of 1034 NL/SPARQL-pairs covering 166 multi-domain knowledge graphs and ontologies.",
    "The queries have a complexity of easy, medium, hard and extra-hard according to the Spider hardness definition (Yu et al., 2018).",
    "Models and parameters",
    "For the experiments we used OpenAI's gpt-3.5-turbo-0125 model.",
    "The average processing time per run (inferencing 1,034 queries of the test set) was 30-40 min."
  ]
}